/**
 * Demo Data IDs
 *
 * Deterministic UUIDs for demo data - allows idempotent seeding.
 * Format: de000000-0000-4000-aXXX-YYYYYYYYYYYY
 *   - "de" prefix = demo
 *   - aXXX = entity type code
 *   - YYYYYYYYYYYY = sequential number
 *
 * Entity Type Codes:
 *   a000 = Firm
 *   a001 = Users
 *   a002 = Clients
 *   a003 = Matters
 *   a004 = Time Entries
 *   a005 = Tasks
 *   a006 = Invoices
 *   a007 = Payments
 *   a008 = Documents
 *   a009 = Notifications
 *   a010 = Calendar Events
 *   a011 = Risk Evaluations
 *   a012 = Compliance Rules
 *   a013 = Emails (AI Inbox)
 *   a014 = Approval Requests
 *   a015 = Task Templates
 *   a016 = Task Template Items
 *   b000 = Uploads (MinIO)
 */

